Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: API rate limiting or blocked requests

Solution: Increase delay between requests in rate_limit_delay settings
Use rotating user agents and implement exponential backoff
Issue: Maltego import fails

Solution: Verify CSV format matches Maltego requirements
Check entity types are valid Maltego entity names
Ensure XML structure follows Maltego schema
Issue: Incomplete data extraction

Solution: Update CSS selectors if LinkedIn changes page structure
Implement fallback selectors for critical data fields
Add logging to identify which fields fail extraction
Issue: Memory errors with large datasets

Solution: Process profiles in smaller batches
Implement streaming JSON parsing for large files
Clear collected data periodically during batch processing
